        '  - For cross-object queries (e.g., Opportunity + accounts_revenue__c), explain how the datasets relate.\n' +
        '  H1/H2 MERGE FOR RANKINGS: When queries are split by time period (H1=Apr-Sep, H2=Oct-Mar):\n' +
